# ============================================================================
# typed-affordance-reasoning — what git does NOT carry.
#
# Big data and model weights are transferred to the lab PC by USB (or
# regenerated there); git carries only code + small committed artifacts
# (raw predictions, the 200 Exp-B bundle images, configs, the paper).
# See the repo README and experiments/*/HOW_TO_RUN_*.md for the transfer list.
# ============================================================================

# ---- Large datasets (USB to the lab PC; never in git) ----------------------
datasets/
ooal_models_amar/
sam_vit_h_4b8939.pth

# ---- Reference PDFs (the .md planning notes ARE kept; drop the binaries) ----
related_work/Initial Papers/
related_work/Learning Affordances Papers/
related_work/XAI Papers/
related_work/*.docx

# ---- Python ----------------------------------------------------------------
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
.ipynb_checkpoints/
*.egg-info/
.venv/
venv/
env/

# ---- Per-call caches (resumable run-state; machine-local, regenerable) -----
**/cache_a_vision/
**/cache_a_local/
**/cache_b/
**/cache_judge/
**/cache_replay/

# ---- Regenerable bundles & auto-downloaded weights -------------------------
# NOTE: experiment_a_bundle/ IS committed (257M, no file >50MB) so the lab PC
# gets it via `git pull` — no USB, no HF re-download. Only its transient out/
# working dir is ignored. To slim the repo later, drop images_full/ (235M,
# regenerable via experiment_a/prep_bundle.sh) and keep instance_seg/+labels.
experiments/experiment_a_bundle/out/
experiments/experiment_b_bundle/out/
experiments/experiment_b/checkpoints/
experiments/experiment_b/legacy/
*.pt
*.pth

# ---- Lab-PC generated outputs (D3 / D4) ------------------------------------
experiments/local_vlms/results/
experiments/local_vlms/vllm_*.log
experiments/ooal_grounding/ooal_upstream/
experiments/ooal_grounding/heatmaps*/
experiments/ooal_grounding/agd_seen_flat/
experiments/ooal_grounding/regions_*.jsonl
experiments/ooal_grounding/out_eval.json

# ---- OS / editor junk ------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*~

# ---- LaTeX build artifacts (keep the .tex/.bib/figures) --------------------
overleaf/*.aux
overleaf/*.log
overleaf/*.out
overleaf/*.bbl
overleaf/*.blg
overleaf/*.synctex.gz
overleaf/*.fdb_latexmk
overleaf/*.fls
